---
title: Sugar Shack Maple-Mustard Pork Chops with Candied Walnuts and Creamy Mashed Potatoes
description: Pork chops slathered in a mustard-maple sauce and topped with crunchy candied walnuts – what more could you want for a delicious, sugar shack-inspired meal?! Crispy broccoli and creamy chive mash? You've got it!
